{"tid":738083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔玻璃心 唔抵得人公屋出身做狀元","createTime":"2018-07-11T09:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T23:42:40.000Z","uid":15711,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e628056673caeb86873f798c77c4922b44b750a2","tid":738083,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:10:33.000Z","msg":"人地努力改變命運關你地鬼事咩"},{"pid":"917794e6dd4a935ee731a7e2934f5ffd62b40870","tid":738083,"uid":173110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:13:57.000Z","msg":"人地討論下又關你鬼事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 酸民"},{"pid":"2ad9a83b3091d9f17bb3b140c0566a3810579902","tid":738083,"uid":159086,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:17:09.000Z","msg":"仁書院（袁瑋謙）<br />\n父母分別為企業顧問及家庭主婦<br />\n<br />\n德望學校（李焯瑩）<br />\n李焯瑩的父親從商，媽媽是一名編輯<br />\n<br />\n喇沙書院（黃子衡）<br />\n自認中產父親從事與電腦有關，而母親則任文員<br />\n<br />\n萃男書院（沈家浩）<br />\n沈家浩的父親從商、母親為家庭主婦<br />\n<br />\n拔萃女書院 ( 林悅兒 )<br />\n父母在大學做文職，媽媽會煲湯水支持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拔萃女書院（梁芷喬 ) <br />\n已獲英國牛津大學有條件取錄，父母是公務員<br />\n<br />\n聖保羅 ( 黃程灝 )<br />\n早於就讀小二時，已通過資優測試跳級<br />\n<br />\n聖保羅( 陸禧 )<br />\n音樂尖子，已有12、3年彈鋼琴經驗，達演奏級水平，則曾參加亞太鋼琴比賽。除了英文外，陸禧所有科目都有補習<br />\n<br />\n聖保羅( 藍正宏 )<br />\n藍正宏稱自己一直想爭取公義、為弱勢發聲及維護香港核心價值。過往亦有與家人參與7.1遊行，他感謝家人毫無保留地支持。<br />\n<br />\n邊幾位係公屋出身做狀元，聽啲師奶講當係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8465c01e4778754e16741ebb6a2f05de5a940b63","tid":738083,"uid":15711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"917794e6dd4a935ee731a7e2934f5ffd62b40870","tid":738083,"uid":173110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:13:57.000Z","msg":"人地討論下又關你鬼事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 酸民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:18:10.000Z","msg":"人地住公屋做狀元佢地又唔抵得，真係可憐"},{"pid":"4865d23df8dd15bb7f830a91dcb786ac46453358","tid":738083,"uid":68097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:19:07.000Z","msg":"child登 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7919d1bb0979197906e83751b8b2db743b807343","tid":738083,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:19:20.000Z","msg":"連登仔係幻想果班人band3學校出身<br />\n點知人地公屋但讀名校 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c3a34027919d908dbd301a95653acca498cc5b","tid":738083,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:19:26.000Z","msg":"公屋有啲人先有錢"},{"pid":"20677b262d5365dabcf92dae9b8c00d0cb5d0ad7","tid":738083,"uid":24339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:20:08.000Z","msg":"這就是連登仔"},{"pid":"3cbdec3539ef722537932cb05d802b3dca699ac8","tid":738083,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:56:16.000Z","msg":"下，唔係有錢人先住公屋咩？"},{"pid":"9d86decf716cf2018582818e27e524d2bdfcaa7f","tid":738083,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T10:40:53.000Z","msg":"玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec9dec9180bbed3f90192afe1fe02590b539f41","tid":738083,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T23:42:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}